# einteract

[![Binder](https://mybinder.org/badge_logo.svg)](https://mybinder.org/v2/gh/asaboor-gh/einteract/HEAD?urlpath=%2Fdoc%2Ftree%2Feinteract-demo.ipynb)
[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/einteract.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/einteract)
[![Downloads](https://pepy.tech/badge/einteract)](https://pepy.tech/project/einteract)

An enhanced interactive widget that let's you observe any trait of widgets, observe multiple functions and build beautiful dashboards. This is a wrapper library around interact functionality in [ipyslides](https://github.com/asaboor-gh/ipyslides) which also provides rich content representations. 

![](interact.png)

See code of this simple yet full customizable dashboard on binder [![Binder](https://mybinder.org/badge_logo.svg)](https://mybinder.org/v2/gh/asaboor-gh/einteract/HEAD?urlpath=%2Fdoc%2Ftree%2Feinteract-demo.ipynb)
